destinationArn.description: ARN of the CloudWatch Logs log group or Kinesis Data Firehose delivery stream to receive access logs. If you specify a Kinesis Data Firehose delivery stream, the stream name must begin with `amazon-apigateway-`. Automatically removes trailing `:*` if present.

format.description:
Formatting and values recorded in the logs.
For more information on configuring the log format rules visit the AWS [documentation](https://docs.aws.amazon.com/apigateway/latest/developerguide/set-up-logging.html)
